    "description": "物聯網 (Internet of Things, IoT) 是近期非常重要也受到高度關注的議題, 主要訴求是\"物物聯網\"或是\"萬物聯網\", 就是將全球物件以及各式各樣的感應器 (sensors) 等等也連上網路, 除了資料與數據收集分析外, 也可以回饋進行各種控制, 這對於未來生活的便利性將有極大的影響",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "(1) 物聯網的基礎架構與創新應用<br>(2) 物聯網感知層/網路層/應用層技術<br>(3) IPv6 協議運作原理與  IPv6 最新發展趨勢<br>(4) IPv4/IPv6 轉移機制<br>(5) 物聯網感測器平台 (Sensor  Node Platforms)<br>(6) 物聯網感測器網路 (Sensors Networks) 的路由協議 (routing protocols)<br>(7) 物聯網無線傳輸技術<br>(8) 物聯網框架標準 (IoT framework)",
        "en": "(1) Introduction to IoT Basic Architectures and Its Innovation Applications <br>(2) Introduction to IoT Sensing Layer/Networking Layer/Application Layer Techniques <br>(3) Introduction to IPv6 Protocols Theory and the State of Arts <br>(4) Introduction to IPv4/IPv6 Transfer Mechanism <br>(5) Introduction to IoT Sensor Nodes Platform <br>(6) Introduction to Routing Protocols of IoT Sensor Networks <br>(7) Introduction to IoT Wireless Communications Techniques <br>(8) Introduction to IoT Frameworks"
    },
